event.title: FSFE with booth, talks and dev room at FOSDEM 2024

body.p: It is that time of the year again. FOSDEM will take place in Brussels on 3 and 4 February 2024. The Free Software Foundation Europe will be there with most of its staff and some of our volunteers!
You can find a detailed overview of FSFE organized dev rooms and workshops in this news item.
We hope to see you at FOSDEM!
